---
import Github from "../contactIcons/Github.astro";
import Instagram from "../contactIcons/Instagram.astro";
import LinkedIn from "../contactIcons/LinkedIn.astro";
import Twitter from "../contactIcons/Twitter.astro";
---

<footer
  class="w-full bg-blue-200 py-14 font-light dark:bg-[#08152C] dark:bg-opacity-40"
>
  <section
    class="lg:container lg:mx-auto items-center px-3 flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-8 md:flex-row md:justify-between lg:px-10"
  >
    <p class="w-full text-sm text-[#0A0C10]/70 dark:text-[#F5F9FF]/50">
      Diseñado en
      <a
        href="https://www.figma.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="text-[#0A0C10] dark:text-[#F5F9FF] hover:text-purple-600 dark:hover:text-[#96F] focus-visible:text-[#90F] transition-all dark:focus-visible:text-[#96F]"
        >Figma</a
      >
       y codificado en
      <a
        href="https://code.visualstudio.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="text-[#0A0C10] dark:text-[#F5F9FF] hover:text-purple-600 dark:hover:text-[#96F] focus-visible:text-[#90F] transition-all dark:focus-visible:text-[#96F]"
        >Visual Studio Code</a
      > por mí mismo. Construido con
      <a
        href="https://astro.build"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="text-[#0A0C10] dark:text-[#F5F9FF] hover:text-purple-600 dark:hover:text-[#96F] focus-visible:text-[#90F] transition-all dark:focus-visible:text-[#96F]"
        >Astro</a
      > y
      <a
        href="https://tailwindcss.com"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="text-[#0A0C10] dark:text-[#F5F9FF] hover:text-purple-600 dark:hover:text-[#96F] focus-visible:text-[#90F] transition-all dark:focus-visible:text-[#96F]"
        >Tailwind CSS</a
      >
       , desplegado en
      <a
        href="https://fly.io"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer"
        class="text-[#0A0C10] dark:text-[#F5F9FF] hover:text-[#90F] focus-visible:text-[#90F] dark:hover:text-[#96F] transition-all dark:focus-visible:text-[#96F]"
        >Fly.io</a
      >
       . Las tipografía utilizada es

      <a
        href="https://www.atipofoundry.com/fonts/n27"
        class="text-[#0A0C10] dark:text-[#F5F9FF] hover:text-[#90F] focus-visible:text-[#90F] dark:hover:text-[#96F] transition-all dark:focus-visible:text-[#96F]"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noreferrer">Aileron</a
      >.
    </p>
    <span class="w-full md:w-10 h-[1px] bg-gray-400 dark:bg-gray-700 md:hidden"
    ></span>
    <div class="w-full flex flex-col gap-2 [&>div]:px-0">
      <p class="text-sm text-[#0A0C10]/70 dark:text-[#F5F9FF]/40">
        2023 Humberto Yupanqui, todos los derechos reservados. FullStack
        Developer, Freelancer.
      </p>
      <div
        class="flex gap-2 justify-center md:justify-start [&>a]:bg-purple-950/5 [&>a]:w-11 [&>a]:h-11 [&>a]:rounded-full [&>a]:p-2.5 [&>a>svg]:w-6 [&>a>svg]:h-6"
      >
        <Github hyperlink="https://github.com/ypnqh" />
        <Instagram />
        <Twitter />
        <LinkedIn />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</footer>
